description: Resubmission application for approval of reserved matters pursuant to condition 1 & 2 of outline planning permission ref: 2001/1894 dated 22-06-2004 relating to detailed design and external appearance with associated landscaping for the mixed used development of the Southern part of the former Timber yard, Riverside Wharf, comprising 10 affordable residential units, 266 private residential units.  500sqm of A3 floor space new access roads, car parking and public open space. The total residential provision of 276 Residential units represent a proportion of the maximum number of 613 residential units allowed across the entire site under application reference 2001 1894. The remainder of the affordable housing is provided to the Northern parcel of the site (Leeside Wharf).
site_name: Altius 2 & 2021 (Lathams Yrd & Leeside And Midd'sex Wharves)
